<h1><marquee><font color="red">INVESTIGATION OF SOCIAL MEDIA</font></marquee></h1>
<P><b>Investigation </b>in social media involves using various techniques to gather information from platform like facebook , twiter , instagram , youtube and tiktok and so on </P>
<p>To uncover insight , trends or evidence related to the particular topic , event or individual.This could including analyzing public posts comments profile and interaction </p>
<p>to understand sentiments , behaviour or patterns , investigater might also employ tools like social network analysis to map connections between users and identify key players </p>
<p>a given context.Ethical consideration privacy concerns and the validate of data are crucial to address when conducting social media investigations</p><br>
